#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Scan_Sort_Ops/histogram.md:0
msgid "# triton.language.histogram"
msgstr "# triton.language.histogram"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Scan_Sort_Ops/histogram.md:2
msgid "## 1. OP 概述"
msgstr "## 1. OP Overview"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Scan_Sort_Ops/histogram.md:4
msgid ""
"简介：基于 input 计算 1 个具有 num_bins 个 bin 的直方图，每个 bin 宽度为 1，起始于 0。\n"
"原型：\n"
msgstr ""
"Introduction: Computes a histogram with `num_bins` bins based on `input`, where each bin has a width of 1, starting from 0.  \n"
"Prototype:\n"

#. type: code
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Scan_Sort_Ops/histogram.md:6
msgid ""
"```python\n"
"triton.language.histogram(\n"
" input,\n"
" num_bins,\n"
" mask=None,\n"
" _semantic=None,\n"
" _generator=None\n"
")\n"
"```\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Scan_Sort_Ops/histogram.md:8
msgid "可以作为tensor的成员函数调用，如`x.histogram(...)`，与`histogram(x, ...)`等效。"
msgstr "Can be called as a member function of a tensor, such as `x.histogram(...)`, which is equivalent to `histogram(x, ...)`."

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Scan_Sort_Ops/histogram.md:10
msgid "## 2. OP 规格"
msgstr "## 2. OP Specifications"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Scan_Sort_Ops/histogram.md:12
msgid "### 2.1 参数说明"
msgstr "### 2.1 Parameter Description"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Scan_Sort_Ops/histogram.md:14
msgid ""
"| 参数名           | 类型                | 说明                                                             |\n"
"| ------------- | ----------------- | -------------------------------------------------------------- |\n"
"| `input`        | `tensor`          | 输入数据，包含需要统计分布的所有数值点                                                    |\n"
"| `num_bins`       | `int`    | 定义要将整个数据范围划分成多少个等宽的区间                       |\n"
"| `mask`     | `int1`或`tensor<int1>`，可选    | 指定数据范围，防止访问越界 |\n"
"| `_semantic`   | -                 | 保留参数，暂不支持外部调用                                                |\n"
"| `_generator` |-                 | 保留参数，暂不支持外部调用\n"
msgstr ""
"| Parameter Name | Type | Description |\n"
"| ------------- | ----------------- | -------------------------------------------------------------- |\n"
"| `input`        | `tensor`          | Input data, containing all numerical points whose distribution is to be counted |\n"
"| `num_bins`       | `int`    | Defines how many equal-width intervals the entire data range should be divided into |\n"
"| `mask`     | `int1` or `tensor<int1>`, optional    | Specifies the data range to prevent out-of-bounds access |\n"
"| `_semantic`   | -                 | Reserved parameter, currently not supported for external calls |\n"
"| `_generator` |-                 | Reserved parameter, currently not supported for external calls |\n"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Scan_Sort_Ops/histogram.md:16
msgid ""
"返回值：\n"
"用tensor表示的直方图\n"
"注：当前triton3.2版本暂未支持mask，待版本更新后支持；input输入范围限制在[0,num_bins-1]中，待版本更新后支持全范围\n"
msgstr ""
"Return value:  \n"
"Histogram represented by tensor  \n"
"\n"
"Note: The current Triton 3.2 version does not yet support mask; support will be added in a future version. The input range is limited to [0, num_bins-1]; full range support will be added in a future version.\n"

