#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Scan_Sort_Ops/histogram.md:32
msgid "### 2.4 使用方法"
msgstr "### 2.4 Usage"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Scan_Sort_Ops/histogram.md:34
msgid "以下示例实现了histogram的调用："
msgstr "The following example demonstrates the invocation of histogram:"

#. type: code
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Scan_Sort_Ops/histogram.md:36
msgid ""
"```python\n"
"@triton.jit\n"
"def histogram_kernel(x_ptr, z_ptr, M: tl.constexpr, N: tl.constexpr):\n"
"    offset1 = tl.arange(0, M)\n"
"    offset2 = tl.arange(0, N)\n"
"    x = tl.load(x_ptr + offset1)\n"
"    z = tl.histogram(x, N)\n"
"    tl.store(z_ptr + offset2, z)\n"
"\n"
"x = torch.randint(0, N, (M, ), device=device, dtype=torch.int32)\n"
"z = torch.empty(N, dtype=torch.int32, device=device)\n"
"histogram_kernel[(1, )](x, z, M=M, N=N)\n"
"```\n"
msgstr ""

